    }
</style> 

legend 
    The LEGEND

    | <#daf7b5> | Artifact |
    | <#f1a3a3> | File |
    | <#c8d4e4> | Node |
    | <#f2f3f3> | Cloud |
    | <#bfeeee> | Database |
    | <#ffffea> | Package |
    | -(0)- | Connection |

endlegend


@enduml